gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin

Class NumericalRangeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.admin.NumericalRangeBuilder

  • public final class NumericalRangeBuilder
extends java.lang.Object

    Builds a NumericalRange from incrementally-specified component parts. This class is useful because NumericalRange is immutable: you must specify all properties in its constructor and you can't use it as a Java bean.

    Per Effective Java Item 17, this class is marked final because it was not designed for inheritance.
